A wireless mesh network (WMN) is a communications network made up of radio nodes organized in a mesh topology. It is also a form of wireless ad hoc network. Wireless mesh networks often consist of mesh clients, mesh routers and gateways.

the controller server for all these access point may be visualized 
and this controller server is the open API if you want you build a custom application built around cisco wireless

